        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1406584653,
        "creation_date": 1406584653,
        "body": "<p>Turns out it was a ProGuard issue. Fixed it by adding the following lines:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>-keepclassmembers class ** {\n    @com.squareup.otto.Subscribe public *;\n    @com.squareup.otto.Produce public *;\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
        "answer_id": 25005028,
        "question_id": 25004921
    }],
